Class Person

java.lang.Object
com.prototype.model.entities.Person
@Entity public class Person extends Object
Entity that represents a person interacting with the system. A person may act as a requester of entry authorizations and is identified by a full name and document number.

This entity is stored in the people table and contains the basic personal and role-related information necessary for access control and auditing processes.
